Write the differnce between soap and restful web service?
 
     
        SOAP                                             REST
1) SOAP is a protocol.                        1) REST is a architectural style
 
2) stands for SIMPLE OBJECT ACCESS            2) stands for REPRESENTATIONAL STATE TRANSFER.
PROTOCOL.
        
3) can't use rest because it is a             3)REST can use SOAP web services becauseit is 
protocol,platform& language independent         a concept & can use any protocol like HTTP,SOAP.

4)SOAP uses services interfaces to expose     4)REST uses URI to expose bussiness logic.
the business logic

5) JAX-WS is a java API for SOAP services.    5)JAX-RS is java API for restfull web services.

6)SOAP defines standards to be strictly       6) not too much standards defined like SOAP.
followed

7)SOAP permits XML data format only.          7)REST permits different data format such as 
                                                Plain text, HTML, XML,JSON,etc.
8)SOAP is less preferred than REST.           8)REST is more preferred than SOAP.

9)SOAP defines its own security.              9)RESTful web services inherits security 
                                                measures from the underlying transport

Q2) what are http methods?

HTTP is a protocol, or a definite set of rules, for 
accessing resources on the web


GET:GET is used to request(only read) data from a specified resource.
POST: we can only read write data
PUT: we can read write and update data

DELETE: use to delete the data.
PATCH:With PATCH, you can update part of a resource 
by simply passing in the data of the field to be updated.
